_sText:
This is a map themed for Veterans day, It is very small in scale and file size.
This map plays very fast and the game play is fun. 

This map is created for a cDS map contest for the month of November.
These contests are to be themed either for holidays within a month or what ever that months competition is.
Anyone is welcome to submit maps, you do not need to be a cDS member.
If you'd like to submit your map please join the cDS forms: http://cyberdeathsquad.com/forums/

Hope you enjoy!
